"use strict";(self.webpackChunk=self.webpackChunk||[]).push([[5269],{66338:e=>{e.exports=JSON.parse('{"Where should it go? Tap the map to place this building.":"要放在哪邊？在地圖上點擊來放置建築物吧。","Cancel Build":"取消建築","Move Map":"移動地圖","Continue":"繼續","Level":"等級","Discord":"Discord","Patreon":"贊助","Get help":"需要協助","Options":"選項","Appearance":"外觀","Runeshop":"商城","Follower":"跟隨者","Change Class":"更換職業","Inventory":"儲藏室","Spells":"法術","Skills":"技能","Status":"狀態","Equipment":"裝備","Party":"隊伍","You do not have any party members. Invite your allies to a party to share experience and fight battles together.":"你現在沒有隊友。邀請你的盟友加入隊伍來一起戰鬥並共享經驗值吧。","Disband party":"解散隊伍","Leave party":"離開隊伍","Are you sure you would like to leave this party?":"你確定要離開這個隊伍?","No":"否","Yes":"確認","Current bonus:":"此加成目前累積威力：","Time left:":"剩下時間:","Character":"角色","Codex":"圖鑑","You have left the party":"你已離開隊伍","Town Development":"城鎮發展","Buildings":"建築","Decorations":"裝飾物","Costs:":"花費:","Build":"建築","Am I building something today?":"今天找我蓋什麼東西嗎？","Aye, traveler.":"是的，旅行者。","Pleasure to meet ye.":"真正高興地見到尼。","The name\'s Gofannon. Samson says you\'ll need my help building out your Origin Town.":"我的名字是哥凡農。參孫說你會需要我來幫忙建造你的初始城鎮。","An Unfelled\'s home is of dire importance. Here, we can build buildings of many a use.":"一個不落者的據點至關重要。看，我們可以蓋些有用的建築。","I\'ll help ye. I\'ll even build ye your first Shop for free. But ye free ride ends there, I\'m afraid.":"我會幫助尼。我甚至可以幫尼免費蓋第一間商店。但是就這一間。","Shall we get started, then?":"那我們就開工啦？","Gofannon":"哥凡農","My name is Samson. And what is yours, traveler?":"我的名字叫做參孫。你呢，旅者?","New character name":"新的角色名稱","Connect Google Play Games":"連結 Google Play Games","Sandbox mode":"沙盒模式","Start at level 250 with a large inventory":"從等級250並持有大量道具的狀態開始","By continuing, you verify that you are at least 13 years of age and agree to the:":"若要繼續操作，你確認自己年滿 13 歲並同意：","privacy policy":"隱私政策","terms of service":"服務條款","If you would like to attach an email address to your character, you can enter it below. We will only use your email address for character recovery options.":"若你想將角色和email地址綁定在一起，就可以在此輸入。我們只會將你的email地址用來做角色還原使用。","Email address (optional)":"Email 地址 (選填)","Promo code (optional)":"優惠代碼(非必要)","When encountering a foe in combat, which of the following are you?":"你是以怎樣的樣態來與敵人戰鬥？","The Warrior":"戰士","High HP and Attack power, low usage of skills.":"高生命值和攻擊力，但鮮少使用技能。","The Mage":"法師","Low HP and Attack power, but higher magical power. High usage of spells.":"低生命值和攻擊力，但魔力高昂。經常使用法術。","The Thief":"盜賊","Moderate HP, high Attack power, moderate magical power. Higher usage of status effects.":"一般般的生命值和魔力，但高攻擊力。較常使用各類狀態效果。","Meet me in Loton, traveler.":"來盧頓見我吧，旅者。","Cancel":"取消","Achievements & Record":"成就&紀錄","Play":"遊玩","Explore the world and fight monsters.":"探索世界並與魔物戰鬥。","Kingdom":"王國","Kingdoms":"王國","View or join a Kingdom.":"查詢或加入王國。","Purchase items or character appearance options from the Runeshop.":"自商城購買物品或角色外觀。","Unfelled Recruitment":"不落者徵才","Earn rewards by inviting your friends to the game.":"邀請你的朋友來玩就能獲得獎勵。","Change your character\'s class, access your inventory, and more.":"改變你的角色職業，查閱你的所有物，和其他功能。","Quests":"任務","Change game settings and options.":"改變遊戲設定和選項。","Title Menu":"主選單","Return to the title screen.":"回到標題畫面。","Event":"活動","Athantia":"亞特南提亞","Athantia is coastal home to the Athantians.":"亞特南提亞為亞特南提亞之民的居所。","Market":"市場","Creatures of the Deep":"深海生物","Athantia Temple":"亞特南提亞聖殿","Avalon":"阿瓦隆","The Kingdom of Avalon is possibly the most well known of Kingdoms, though much of its influence is long lost.":"即使阿瓦隆王國已逐漸式微，但仍是最為人知曉的王國。","Avalon Market":"阿瓦隆市場","Odds & Ends":"零碎之物","Smith of Avalon":"阿瓦隆的鐵匠","Lady by the Lake":"湖濱麗人","Merlin\'s Apprentices":"梅林塾","Avalon Herbalist":"阿瓦隆藥劑師","Balor":"巴羅爾","The dark and volcanic land of the forces of Balor.":"巴羅爾軍勢的爆炎之地。","Odin\'s Forge":"奧丁之鍛造","Balor Spells":"巴羅爾法術屋","Balor Beasts":"巴羅爾獸屋","Prometheus\'s Workbench":"普羅米修斯的工作檯","Demeter\'s Rest":"狄蜜特的居所","A quiet village at the foot of the gods.":"眾神腳邊的閑靜村莊。","Demeter\'s Rest Inn":"狄蜜特之鄉的民宿","Demeter\'s Rest Hall":"狄蜜特之鄉市政廳","Fishing Hut":"釣魚小屋","The humble home of a great angler.":"垂釣大師的小屋。","Forest Clearing":"森林空地","A small clearing in Loton Woods.":"盧頓森林中的一小塊空地。","Origin Town":"初始城鎮","Where it all began.":"一切都從這裡開始。","Your Home":"你家","Jotunheim":"約頓海姆","Jotunheim was once land to the giants. It is now a home to those they left behind.":"曾為巨人之地的約頓海姆，如今成為被遺棄之人的家園。","Songs of the Giants":"巨人之歌","Larger Than Life":"大於生命","Mountain Bestiary":"山中寵物店","Mountain\'s Rest":"那山之餘","Loton":"盧頓","Loton is a humble and simple village.":"盧頓乃是個平凡無奇的小村莊。","General Store":"普通的店鋪","Loton Town Hall":"盧頓市政廳","New Lyonesse":"新里昂內斯","Snowy land of Lyonesse, a Kingdom of divinity and grace.":"聖潔的國度里昂內斯的冰封之地。","Northern Trader":"北族商人","Bright Smith":"亮白鐵匠","Sacred Jewels":"神聖珠寶商","Divine Beasts":"聖潔猛獸","Lyonesse Grounds":"里昂內斯領地","Lythryn":"萊斯林","Home of the elves. Humans may not find it welcoming.":"精靈的家園。人類在此可能不太受歡迎。","Elven Alchemist":"精靈煉金工坊","Jeweller of the Woods":"林間寶石商","Myrkheim":"米爾克海姆","Myrkheim is the underground home of the dwarven people.":"矮人們在地底下的居所，即為米爾克海姆。","Myrkheim Trader":"米爾克海姆商人","Myrkheim Bazaar":"米爾克海姆市集","Nothren Settlement":"北族聚落","Nothren, muddy land of those who run with beasts.":"北族之地，與猛獸爭生存的人們所居之地。","Trader":"行商","Brokkr\'s Forge":"布洛克的鍛冶屋","Freyja\'s Followers":"弗蕾亞的跟隨者","The South Rest":"小南旅宿","Nothren Town Hall":"北族市政廳","Onogoro":"淤能碁呂","Secret island of Onogoro. ":"神秘的淤能碁呂之島。 ","Field Bestiary":"荒野寵物店","Resting Place":"休憩處","A forest clearing, tribute to one that is lost.":"森林中被清理出來的一塊空地，紀念迷失的人。","Suddun":"蘇頓","A land of traders and appreciators of the finer things, Suddun lies to the East.":"蘇頓位於東方，那是個滿有行商與鑑定行家的土地。","Suddun Market":"蘇頓市場","Suddun Bazaar":"蘇頓市集","The Sands":"沙海","Suddun Bestiary":"蘇頓寵物店","The Oasis Jewels":"綠洲寶石","Svarga":"斯瓦加","A quiet fishing town, Svarga lists along the great Svarga river.":"斯瓦加位於斯瓦加河畔，是個寧靜的漁村。","Svarga Smith":"斯瓦加鐵匠鋪","Svarga Bestiary":"斯瓦加寵物店","Titan Workshop":"泰坦工坊","One of the few remaining structures abandoned by the Olympians.":"奧林匹亞眾神遺留下的少數建築之一。","Vinland":"文蘭","To the North lies Vinland, a town of wealth.":"財富之都文蘭，地處於北方。","Vinland Beasts":"文蘭野獸","Rose\'s Rest":"蘿絲旅宿","Origin":"原始","Loton Woods":"盧頓森林","Great Plains":"大平原","The Outskirts":"郊區","Lythryn Woods":"萊斯林之森","Great Athantia":"大亞特南提亞","Suddun Dunes":"蘇頓沙丘","Suddun Desert":"蘇頓沙漠","Kingdom of Avalon":"阿瓦隆王國","The Great Bridge":"巨橋","Valhalla\'s Cradle":"瓦爾哈蘭搖籃","Myrkheim Mines":"米爾克海姆礦脈","Myrkheim Descent":"米爾克海姆低地","Mountains of Jotunheim":"約頓海姆山脈","Winter Path":"寒冬之路","Northern Reaches":"北達境","Lakes of Lyonesse":"里昂內斯之湖","Depths of Balor":"巴羅爾深處","Channels of Balor":"巴羅爾隧道","Fallen God\'s Rest":"墮落神祇之巢","Olympia Trails":"奧林匹亞棧道","Lost Kingdom of Olympia":"奧林匹亞的失落王國","Forest Gate":"森林隘口","Proving Grounds":"試驗地","Woven Forest":"編織森林","Valley of the Gods":"眾神之谷","Onogoro Island":"淤能碁呂島","Fen Lagoon":"沼澤潟湖","Fen Halls":"芬薩利爾","Odin\'s Finger":"奧丁之指","Dragon\'s Foot":"龍之足","Great Athantia East":"大亞特南提亞東部","Old Lyonesse":"古里昂內斯","Meropis":"麥若普斯","Valhalla Bay":"瓦爾哈拉海灣","Asphodel Meadows":"常世花平野","Asphodel Trails":"常世花棧道","A Mushroom of Perilous Visitation":"一朵看起來危險的蕈類","Giant\'s Abyss":"巨人深淵","Northern Battlegrounds":"北方戰場","Underworld Portal":"冥府之門","Beast Den":"野獸巢穴","Watcher\'s Tomb":"守望者之墓","Great Desert Tomb":"大漠之墓","Chaos Portal":"混沌之門","Dragon Roost":"巨龍宿巢","Goblin Fortress":"哥布林要塞","Shaded Cave":"暗影洞窟","Western Battlegrounds":"西方戰場","Bells of Olympia":"奧林匹亞之鐘","Fallen Champion\'s Clearing":"墮落冠軍之處","Jotunheim Arena":"約頓海姆競技場","West Suddun Arena":"西蘇頓競技場","Nothren Sparring Grounds":"北方戰亂之地","Old Lyonesse Arena":"古里昂內斯競技場","Arena of the Gods":"眾神競技場","Volcanic Arena":"火山競技場","Lythryn Arena":"萊斯林競技場","Signpost":"路標","↑ Jotunheim Mountains":"↑ 約頓海姆山脈","Lythryn Woods → No humans allowed!":"萊斯林森林 → 人族滾蛋！","Fallen Champion\'s Clearing ↑":"墮落冠軍之處 ↑","Great Athantia →":"大亞特南提亞 →","← Mountains of Jotunheim":"← 約頓海姆山脈","Giant Head":"巨人之首","Head of ?, Great Giant.":"未知巨人之首。","Head of Gymir, Great Giant.":"偉大巨人蓋密爾之首。","Head of Eistla, Great Giant.":"偉大巨人艾斯特拉之首。","Head of Yagyr, Great Giant.":"偉大巨人雅吉爾之首。","Head of Daga, Great Giant.":"偉大巨人妲嘎之首。","Head of Lamyr, Great Giant.":"偉大巨人拉米爾之首。","Northern Reaches. Lyonesse ↑":"北達境。里昂內斯 ↑","Pillar":"柱子","Old Lyonesse, lain in ruins.":"古里昂內斯，靜躺於廢墟之中。","Kingdom of Avalon ↓":"阿瓦隆王國 ↓","← Deserts of Suddun":"← 蘇頓沙漠","Wrong way!":"走錯路啦！","← The Great Bridge":"← 大橋","← Myrkheim Mines":"← 米爾克海姆礦脈","Svarga →":"斯瓦加 →","The Great Plains ↑":"大平原 ↑","Vinland ↑ Lythryn Woods →":"文蘭 ↑ 萊斯林森林 →","Fen Halls →":"芬薩利爾 →","Tower of Oceanus":"奧克亞諾斯之塔","Tower of Selene":"塞勒涅之塔","Tower of Themis":"泰美斯之塔","Tower of Eos":"愛奧斯之塔","Tower of Prometheus":"普羅米修斯之塔","Last Message":"最後的訊息","I still remember the day that mother told us we must go. Our towers were crumbling and our sky was falling. I didn\'t want it to end. I didn\'t want to leave home.":"我還記得母親要我們必須離開的那天。我們的塔正在塌陷，我們的天空正在墜落。我不想要這一切結束，我不想要離開我的家鄉。","But they were jealous -- all of them! We didn\'t want power. They did! We only sought knowledge. We only sought peace.":"但他們嫉妒，他們所有人都嫉妒！我們不想要力量，他們才是！我們只渴求知識，我們只訴求和平。","The Jotunheim. The Elysian. The Balor. They came for us. They wanted our magics. They wanted our sky. They tore everything down. They hunted our Titans.":"那些約頓海姆人。那些淨土之民。那些巴羅爾人。他們找到我們，奪取我們的魔法，掠奪我們的天空，還摧毀了一切，獵殺了我們的泰坦。","If you are reading this, you have found our home. I hope there is something left. I hope our guardians have protected our Titans. I hope to find my brother again.":"如果你看到這個訊息，那你已經找到了我們的家。我希望還有東西剩下。我希望我們的守護者保護了我們的泰坦。我希望能再次找到我的兄弟。","We\'re gone now.":"我們已經走了。","Loton Forest Gate":"盧頓森林之門","Lythryn Gate":"萊斯林之門","Athantia Gate":"亞特南提亞之門","Suddun East Gate":"蘇頓東門","Suddun West Gate":"蘇頓西門","Avalon Gate":"阿瓦隆之門","Valhalla\'s Gate":"瓦爾哈拉之門","Myrkheim Gate":"米爾克海姆之門","Door to Olympia":"奧林匹亞之門","Balor Gate":"巴羅爾之門","Olympia Gate":"奧林匹亞之門","Jotunheim Gate":"約頓海姆之門","Gate of the Gods":"眾神之門","The Lyon\'s Gate":"里昂之門","Island Gate":"島嶼之門","Fen Halls Gate":"芬薩利爾之門","Champion\'s Gate":"冠軍之門","Ferry to Onogoro":"淤能碁呂渡口","Ferry to Meropis":"麥若普斯渡口","Asphodel Gate":"常世花之門","Warp here":"傳送","Last visit:":"前次造訪：","Travel here":"造訪至此","Waygates found in the world may be returned to at will.":"在世界地圖上找到的傳送門可以隨時回來。","Can be used in:":"可使用於：","The Wilds":"荒野","A region of Aethric between towns.":"阿薩力克世界中城鎮間的區域。","Aethric":"阿薩力克","Towns":"城鎮","Dungeons":"地城","You are not ready to venture forth.":"你還沒有準備好繼續冒險。","Leave":"離開","Are you sure you would like to return to the main menu?":"你確定要返回主選單嗎？","You may not be ready for the challenges in this region.":"你大概還沒準備好面對這地區的挑戰。","Leave Area":"離開區域","Main Menu":"主選單","Chat":"聊天","Resume Journey":"重啟旅程","Items":"物品","Tower":"塔","Map":"地圖","New game":"New game","Load game":"Load game","Recover character":"還原角色","Enter your email address or username below. An email will be sent to the character\'s email address containing a code to recover your character.":"輸入你的email地址或角色名稱。一封內含有還原代碼的email將會寄出讓你能還原角色。","Username or email address":"角色名稱或email地址","Enter a code":"輸入代碼","Submit":"提交","Enter the character recovery code that your received via email below.":"輸入你在此 email 收到的還原碼。","Code":"代碼","Please complete all fields":"請填寫所有資料欄位","Please enter a valid recovery code":"請輸入有效的還原碼","Recovery code activated":"啟用還原碼","Loading town...":"城鎮讀取中...","Return to World Map":"回到世界地圖","Worker":"工人","Be careful when traveling at night.":"走夜路要小心。","Different foes will show themselves.":"會有不同的敵人出現。","Villager":"鄉民","Is it raining outside of town?":"城鎮外正在下雨嗎？","I heard you may encounter different monsters when the weather is different.":"我聽說你可能會在不同的天候遭遇不同的怪物。","Helpful Bard":"樂於助人的吟遊詩人","If you see treasure chests on the ground, make sure you open them before your friends do.":"如果你在地上看到寶箱，先開先贏。","Noble":"貴族","Find a piece of armor you like? The Blacksmith will make it the best it can be. Alchemists and Jewellers can add adornments to it.":"有看到你喜歡的護甲嗎？鐵匠可以讓它登峰造極。煉金工房和珠寶商可以為其添加裝飾品。","Svargan":"斯瓦加人","Welcome to Svarga, our town on the Svarga River.":"歡迎來到斯瓦加，我們在斯瓦加河上的城鎮。","The elves of Lythryn lies to the North of here.":"萊斯林的精靈位於這裡的北方。","To be honest, they don\'t appreciate outsiders.":"說實話，他們不喜歡外人。","Athantian":"亞特南提亞人","Hi! Welcome to Athantia.":"你好！歡迎來到亞特南提亞。","Pay a visit to our temple while you\'re here.":"你一定要去看看我們的寺廟。","That Pythia...What a weird lady.":"那個皮媞亞... 真是個奇怪的女人。","I wonder why she\'s here.":"我搞不懂為什麼她要來這裡。","Please visit our temple every day.":"請每天都來參拜我們的寺廟。","Hi!":"嗨！","Angler":"釣客","Heilsa. Welcome to my humble shop.":"日安。歡迎光臨敝店。","Us Svargans only accept coral for our goods. Bring me your best catch and I can reward you plenty.":"我們斯瓦加人只用珊瑚來交易我們的貨物。給我帶些好料來，我會回報你的。","Lythryn Elf":"萊斯林精靈","Welcome to Lythryn.":"歡迎來到萊斯林。","...":" ","We don\'t see many humans here.":"我們不太常看到人類。","How did you make it through our forest?":"你怎麼穿過我們的森林的？","Citizen":"市民","This is the Kingdom of Avalon.":"這是阿瓦隆王國。","It was once a great Kingdom, before the Fallen took most of our people.":"在大墮落帶走我們許多人民之前，它曾經是個偉大的國家。","And our dear King...":"以及我們親愛的王...","Squire":"見習騎士","Some day, I will be a great Knight of Avalon.":"遲早有一天，我會成為一個強大的阿瓦隆騎士。","Just like Sir Balin.":"就像是巴林爵士。","Aspiring Court Mage":"有抱負的宮廷法師","Our Arcanist learns new spells quite often.":"我們的奧術法師經常學習新法術。","Visit Merlin\'s Apprentices every day if you are looking to learn something new.":"如果你想學習新事物就每天來梅林塾看看吧。","Court Mage":"宮廷法師","I was once a Court Mage of Arthus\'s court.":"在下曾是亞瑟王手下的宮廷法師。","He was a great King, honestly.":"說真的，他以前是一位偉大的君主。","Jotunn":"約頓人","Well met.":"哩賀。","Welcome to what is left of the Kingdom of Jotunheim":"歡迎來到約頓海姆王國殘存的部分","We Jotunns are followers of the great giants.":"我們約頓人是偉大巨人們的追隨者。","They are but a memory now.":"他們現在已成追憶。","Visit our Arcanist while you are here. They may be able to teach you a trick or two.":"在你停留的期間多去拜訪我們的奧術師。他們可能會教你些技巧。","The Giant\'s Abyss can be found East of here.":"巨人深淵就在這裡的東邊。","\'tis a dangerous dungeon created by our ancestors.":"它是我們祖先創造的危險迷宮。","Merchant":"商人","Suddun is a land of trade.":"蘇頓是個貿易之都。","There isn\'t much for agriculture in the desert, but we\'ve got plenty else to offer to our neighbors in Aethric.":"沙漠中沒有什麼農業活動，但我們有很多其他東西可以提供給我們住在阿薩力克的鄰居。","Have coin? You\'ve come to the right place. Visit the Bazaar often to see its unique wares.":"你有帶錢嗎？那你來對地方了。經常去市集看看那些獨特的商品。","Wandering One":"遊蕩者","Well, hello.":"喔，你好啊。","Lost Memory":"失落記憶","Demonsmith":"惡魔工匠","If ye gold the materials, I can Demonforge any Masterforged gear ye might \'ve.":"如果尼尤材料，偶可以魔改尼有的匠改裝備。","But it\'ll cost ye.":"霸特，會花尼不少錢。","And if ye don\'t have the gold, I\'ve no use for ye.":"啊尼如果妹有錢，偶幫不鳥尼欸。","Ye ain\'t of our kind.":"尼跟偶又不熟。","Nothren Villager":"北族村民","It is rumored that we Nothren came here from the far east, atop ships of great height and stature.":"謠傳說我們北族從遠東而來，搭乘的是巨大的船隻。","Contrary to our name, we are not from the North.":"和我們的名字不同，我們不是來自北方。","Nothren Valkyrie":"北族女武神","The Nothren are a long line of those who tame beasts.":"北族是一群馴服野獸的人。","If you are to learn our ways, your bond with your follower will grow quite strong.":"如果你學會我們的方法，你和跟隨者的羈絆會更強大。","Nothren Berserker":"北族狂戰士","\'ve no time for you.":"沒空理你。","Aye. Welcome to Nothren, traveler.":"是的。歡迎來到北族地，旅者。","Dog":"狗狗","(Pet the dog?)":"(要嚕狗嗎？)","(You pet the dog.)":"(你嚕了狗。)","(The dog happily wags its tail.)":"(狗狗開心的搖著尾巴。)","Direwolf":"恐狼","(Pet the wolf?)":"(要嚕狼嗎？)","(You pet the wolf.)":"(你嚕了狼。)","(The wolf does not seem happy.)":"(狼狼看起來不太開心。)","(The wolf seems happy.)":"(狼狼看起來蠻開心的。)","Wolf":"狼","(It bit you.)":"(他咬了你。)","Warning:":"警告:","Your PvP equipment loadout appears to be missing a weapon or armor.":"你的競技場裝備似乎缺少武器或裝甲。","Your PvP equipment loadout appears to be missing skills or spells.":"你的PvP裝備設置似乎缺少了技能或法術。","Opponents available:":"可配對的對手:","Hold to Spar":"長按以陪練","Contacting game servers...":"正在連線至伺服器...","Waygate Found":"發現傳送門","You can now freely return to this place from your world map.":"現在你可以自由地從世界地圖上返回此地。","Tap to enter":"點擊入內","Tap to read":"點擊讀取","You must move closer.":"你可以再靠近點。","Year:":"年分：","1004 DCE":"1004 DCE","What is your name, traveler?":"旅者阿，該怎麼稱呼您呢？","Choose your class":"選擇你的職業","Body A":"造型 A","Body B":"造型 B","You may add a recovery email address in case you lose or reset your device. This step is optional.":"你能輸入還原用的email以防你遺失或重置設備。這步驟是選填的。","If you have a promo code, you may enter it below. Otherwise, please leave this option blank.":"如果你有優惠碼，你可以在下方輸入。否則，請將此選項保持空白。","The Land of Aethric":"阿薩力克世界","Upon leaving this forest clearing, you will be placed on the World Map.":"在離開這片森林空地之後，你將會身處於世界地圖中。","These lands are quite large, and you may find traversing them a bit slower than what you are used to thus far.":"這些土地相當廣大，你可能會發現在其中遊歷會比你迄今為止所習慣的要緩慢。","These lands are also full of dangerous creatures.":"這些土地充滿了危險的生物。","You must now meet Samson in the nearby town of Loton to begin your journey.":"你必須在附近的盧頓鎮與參孫見面好開始你的旅程。","Goblin":"哥布林","Battle":"戰鬥","A Goblin blocks your path. Defeat it to continue your journey.":"一隻哥布林擋住了你的路。哥布林必須死。打敗牠以繼續你的旅程。","Tutorial":"教學","You awake in a forest clearing. Your memory is a little blurry.":"你在森林空地上醒來。你的記憶有點模糊。","Drag your finger across the ground to look around.":"使用你的手指拉動地圖來查看周遭。","Ahead of you lie a number of Epitaphs. Interact with them to recall your memory.":"你的前方散落著數個墓誌銘。和它們互動來回想起你的記憶。","A Goblin blocks your path ahead. Defeat it to begin your journey.":"一隻哥布林擋住了你的路。哥布林必須死。打敗牠以開始你的旅程。","Warrior":"戰士","A melee class who favors physical attacks and brute strength over magic. It can wield heavier weapons and armor.":"一個近戰職業，比起魔法，他們更喜歡物理攻擊和蠻力。 它可以穿戴較重的武器和裝甲。","Mage":"法師","A skilled individual who favors magic over strength. It can wield staves and robes.":"擅長使用魔法更甚於力量的專家。他可以使用法杖與長袍。","Thief":"盜賊","A tricky fighting class that favors speed and damage over defense. It can wield light armor, daggers, bows.":"擅長速度及傷害更甚於防禦的狡猾格鬥家。他可以使用輕裝甲，匕首，弓箭。","Epitaph":"墓誌銘","Svarga Port / Dragon\'s Wing":"斯瓦加港 / 龍之翼","Avalon Adventurer\'s Guild":"阿瓦隆冒險者公會","Hellfire Adventurer\'s Guild":"獄炎冒險者公會","Demeter\'s Adventurers":"狄蜜特的冒險者","Northern Adventurer\'s Guild":"北方冒險者公會","Lythryn Adventurer\'s Guild":"萊斯林冒險者公會","Underground Adventurer\'s Guild":"地底冒險者公會","Suddun Adventurer\'s Guild":"蘇頓冒險者公會","Svarga Adventurer\'s Guild":"斯瓦加冒險者公會","Use the directional joystick to move your character.":"使用方向鍵來移動你的角色。","Additionally, you can hold your finger down on a location for 1 second to set a manual destination.":"另外你也能長按在某處一秒來手動設定終點。","Forgotten Forest":"遺落之森","A forest forgotten to the world.":"一座被世界所遺忘的森林。","Circle of Anguish":"煎熬輪迴","Giant\'s Adventurer Guild":"巨人的冒險者公會","Forgotten Isle":"遺落小島","Forgotten Isle Gate":"遺落小島之門","Training Arena":"訓練競技場","Practice combat, collect souls, earn gold, and find unique items by sparring with AI controlled characters in this practice arena.":"在訓練競技場裡與AI控制的角色練習戰鬥，收穫靈魂，賺取金幣，以及獲得獨特物品。","In this arena, you will be matched against AI controlled players that are at similar level in the game as yourself. If you find them to be challenging, you may need to upgrade your equipment.":"在這個競技場中，你將會與AI所控制並且等級相近的玩家角色進行戰鬥。如果你覺得獲勝有困難，也許需要提升你的裝備。","Blade\'s Landing":"鋒刃之地","Training grounds of the great Blades of Finesse PvP Guild.":"芬尼斯之刃PvP公會的練習場所。","Blades of Finesse Guild Hall":"芬尼斯之刃公會大廳","Olympian Ruins":"奧林匹亞廢墟","Onogoro Woods":"淤能碁呂樹林","Hobgoblin Fortress":"巨型哥布林要塞","The Depths":"深層","Monumental Guild":"紀念碑公會","Guild Hall of the Monumental Guild.":"紀念碑公會大廳。","Monumental Guild Hall":"紀念碑公會大廳","Monument of Demeter":"狄蜜特紀念碑","Monument of Thor":"索爾紀念碑","Monument of Ithra":"以斯拉紀念碑","Monument of Vulcan":"瓦肯紀念碑","Meropis Gate":"麥若普斯之門","Leave review":"留下評論","Map Options":"地圖選項","Show player":"顯示玩家","Show monsters":"顯示怪物","Show bosses":"顯示頭目","Show NPCs":"顯示NPC","Show Raids":"顯示副本","Show items":"顯示物品","Show compass":"顯示羅盤","If a character matches the username or email given, an email will be sent to the recovery email address registered to that character.":"如果角色名字與被給予的電子郵件地址相符，一封電子郵件將會被送至該信箱以回復角色。","If you do not receive an email, then it is likely that no recovery email was attached to the character. Please reach out to support at help@playorna.com for help attaching an email address to a lost character.":"如果你沒有收到電子郵件，那角色或許沒有設定復原郵件地址。請聯絡客服(help@playorna.com)來為遺失的角色設定復原郵件地址。","You are unable to interact with this object at this time.":"你現在無法與此物品互動。","All stats":"全屬性","No giver":"沒有人要給","Defeat {monster}":"討伐 {monster}"}')}}]);